imdb.plot outline: Each episode explores the fascinating "secrets" of one scientist or engineer, like the micro-biologist who moonlights as a professional wrestler or the bio-chemist who is also a beauty queen. Subjects include renowned scientists such as Neil deGrasse Tyson, Michio Kaku, Judy Lee, Colin Angle, Mark Siddall, Gavin Schmidt, and Nate Ball. These intimate and funny videos engage viewers with cutting-edge research and fantastic experiments, while also answering questions like "Can string theory explain Brian Boitono?" and "Could you beat Bill Nye in an arm wrestling match?"
